          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Voluntary Protection Program Act</b></p> <p> This bill directs the Department of Labor to establish a program that encourages the establishment of comprehensive safety and health management systems to protect employees from occupational hazards. Labor must also establish a voluntary protection program that encourages excellence and recognizes its achievement in both the technical and managerial protection of employees from occupational hazards.</p>]]></text>
